title: The Pink Floyd Chamber Suite
description:
The songs of Pink Floyd are reinterpreted as classical music in this 2003 concert release from Rock Classics Ltd. Classic Rock String Quartet: Tribute to Pink Floyd includes renditions of "Set the Controls for the Heart of the Sun," "Shine on You Crazy Diamond," "Comfortably Numb," and several others.
Full performer name: The Classic Rock String Quartet.
Arranger: Iain Jennings.

Screen Ratio 1,33:1
Subtitles: Dutch; French; German; Italian; Japanese; Spanish
Audio Tracks:
 Dolby Digital 5.1
 Dolby Digital Stereo
 DTS 5.1
Running time: 59 mins
